groupSpecs.name: Marketing Information
groupSpecs.value: Streamlined and high-leverage design with sure-gripping, cross-hatched knurled jaws. Rivet is closer to the cutting edge for 46% greater cutting and gripping power than other plier designs. Cuts ACSR, screws, nails and most hardened wire. Induction-hardened cutting knives for long life. Hot-riveted joint ensures smooth action and no handle wobble.
